# G2P Pronunciation Dictionaries and Lexicons

A curated list of resources for pronunciation dictionaries, lexicons, and phonetic data across various languages.

## Table of Contents

1. [CC-CEDICT](#cc-cedict)
2. [IPA-Dict](#ipa-dict)
3. [Wiktionary](#wiktionary)
4. [PHOIBLE 2.0](#phoible-20)
5. [Chinese Dialect Lexicons](#chinese-dialect-lexicons)
6. [Danish Pronunciation Dictionary](#danish-pronunciation-dictionary)
7. [English Pronunciation Dictionary](#english-pronunciation-dictionary)
8. [Swedish Pronunciation Dictionary](#swedish-pronunciation-dictionary)
9. [Spanish Pronunciation Dictionary](#spanish-pronunciation-dictionary)
10. [Wikipron](#wikipron)

---

## CC-CEDICT

- **Website**: [cc-cedict.org](https://cc-cedict.org/wiki/)
- **Description**: An open-source Chinese-English dictionary providing translations from Chinese (Mainland and Taiwan), Japanese, and Korean to English. Also includes Chinese to German and French translations.

---

## IPA-Dict

- **Repository**: [GitHub - open-dict-data/ipa-dict](https://github.com/open-dict-data/ipa-dict)
- **Languages**: 29
- **Description**: A collection of pronunciation dictionaries with IPA transcriptions for multiple languages.

---

## Wiktionary

- **Website**: [Wiktionary IPA Pronunciations](https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Category:Terms_with_IPA_pronunciation_by_language)
- **Description**: A comprehensive resource for language spelling and pronunciation, providing IPA pronunciations for terms across all languages.

---

## PHOIBLE 2.0

- **Website**: [phoible.org](https://phoible.org/)
- **Languages**: 3,020
- **Description**: A database of phonological inventories from languages around the world, totaling over 3,000 languages.

---

## Chinese Dialect Lexicons

- **Repository**: [GitHub - CjangCjengh/chinese-dialect-lexicons](https://github.com/CjangCjengh/chinese-dialect-lexicons)
- - **Dialects**: 26
- **Description**: A collection of lexicons for various Chinese dialects, providing valuable resources for dialectal studies.

---

## Danish Pronunciation Dictionary

- **Website**: [OpenSLR - Resource #8](https://www.openslr.org/8/)
- **Description**: A pronunciation dictionary for Danish, generated using eSpeak. Useful for speech recognition and synthesis applications.

---

## English Pronunciation Dictionary

- **Website**: [OpenSLR - Resource #14](https://www.openslr.org/14/)
- **Description**: A British English pronunciation dictionary, suitable for speech processing tasks and linguistic research.

---

## Swedish Pronunciation Dictionary

- **Website**: [OpenSLR - Resource #29](https://www.openslr.org/29/)
- **Description**: A pronunciation dictionary for Swedish, useful for various applications in speech technology.

---

## Spanish Pronunciation Dictionary

- **Website**: [OpenSLR - Resource #34](https://www.openslr.org/34/)
- **Description**: A pronunciation dictionary for Spanish, aiding in speech recognition and synthesis.

---

## Wikipron

- **Repository**: [GitHub - CUNY-CL/wikipron](https://github.com/CUNY-CL/wikipron/tree/master/data/scrape/tsv)
- **Description**: A large collection of pronunciations scraped from Wiktionary, covering a wide range of languages with IPA transcriptions.

---

Feel free to explore these resources for your linguistic, computational, or educational projects!